trans-unit.source: Adadelta is a more robust extension of Adagrad that adapts learning rates based on a moving window of gradient updates, instead of accumulating all past gradients. This way, Adadelta continues learning even when many updates have been done. Compared to Adagrad, in the original version of Adadelta you don't have to set an initial learning rate. In this version, initial learning rate can be set, as in most other Keras optimizers.
trans-unit.target: Adadelta 是 Adagrad 的一个更稳健的扩展,它基于梯度更新的移动窗口来调整学习率,而不是累积所有过去的梯度。这样一来,即使已经做了很多更新,Adadelta 仍会继续学习。与Adagrad相比,在Adadelta的原始版本中,你不必设置初始学习率。在这个版本中,可以设置初始学习率,就像大多数其他Keras优化器一样。

trans-unit.source: Adadelta optimization is a stochastic gradient descent method that is based on adaptive learning rate per dimension to address two drawbacks:
trans-unit.target: Adadelta优化是一种随机梯度下降法,它是基于单位维度自适应学习率来解决两个缺点。

trans-unit.source: Adadelta optimization is a stochastic gradient descent method that is based on adaptive learning rate per dimension to address two drawbacks: 1) the continual decay of learning rates throughout training 2) the need for a manually selected global learning rate
trans-unit.target: Adadelta优化是一种随机梯度下降法,它基于每个维度的自适应学习率来解决两个缺点。1)在整个训练过程中学习率的持续衰减 2)需要手动选择全局学习率。
